      ],
      "name": "Sticky 86993"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### 🧠 Models\n\n**Azure OpenAI** is wired as the default. To demo another provider, connect its node to the agent's *Chat Model* port instead — Ollama (local, no API key), Gemini, OpenAI, or Anthropic.\n\nKeys come from the deployment `.env`; a red node just means that provider's key wasn't supplied.",
        "width": 560,
        "height": 220,
        "color": 5
